highlights.text: “Tung Tung Tung Sahur” by DJ Tralalero Tralala is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Vietnam, up 21 spots at #41.
EM XINH "SAY HI" has the most spots on Viral Songs Vietnam. “NGƯỜI ĐẦU TIÊN” is the highest at #7.
“愛人錯過” by 告五人 has been on Viral Songs Vietnam the longest, at 215 days straight.
“Perfect Pair” by R.L. Beats is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Vietnam at #48.
